<br>
The message I got out of the new rules/proposal was to get more dates in the planes. From Rewena's post about Posting Entities there is 42 total guilds or alliances posting on the Calendar. Many of those are probably not there or eligable to post under the old rules, let alone the new. I say this because some guilds are not even listed as a guild, just a code and some dont list how many planable players they have. Some list players but not enough.  With some easy investigation and some work all the guilds could be confirmed on their eligability to post.<br>
<br>
With the guilds who posted their numbers already, the posting entities stands at 26 (under old rule of needing at least 18 planable members). The average month has 28 days, that means every posting entity can take 1 day in Hate, 1 day in Fear and there is still 2 days left in each plane. Plus we haven't even mentioned Sky. To be honest since I run the raids for my guild, I only post 1 a month because organizing 2 in one month stresses me out to much.<br>
<br>
I just think instead of changing everything around to knock people out of the calendar, we should clean up what we have now. Confirm that people really do have the minimum people needed under the old rules. Those extra days will show up if we do this. This is part of the Calendar Admins job is it not? Investigating the posting entities. I know a lot of people just want to play once they log on, but the Admins need to put that extra effort into looking into things while they are on-line.<br>
<br>
Getting rid of the 2/3 rule is a great idea and as I said I can live with the only 6 from another guild rule.<br>
<br>
If we free up some of the posting entities the extra days wont be needed and I really do like the 2 training days idea Edwina threw out there.<br>
<br>
Usal Rahl<br>
Guardians of Lore</font><P><i>If you are not confused, you do not truely know what is going on</i><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/utitusdivinitus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Titus Divinitus</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Toede</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>16</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>11/6/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFF00>11:07:37 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Proposal.</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I agree with the rules with some considerations:<br>
