<br>
I feel that we need to have admins IN PLACE before we make any changes or the whole excercise is a waste of time.<br>
<br>
I still feel Big Brothers will never be called if you up the number to 40... but I hope to be proven wrong. If I am right though, the original proposal's only effect is to allow &quot;Big Brother&quot; guilds to post 2 day raids instead of singles - interesting.<br>
